c: 12
v: 66
t: "(Uyise) wathi, “angisoze neze ngamthumela kanye nani kuze kube ninginika isithembiso (isifungo) ngoMvelinqangi ukuthi nizombuyisela kumina ngaphandle uma nizungelezwe (izitha)” ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebemnikile isithembiso sabo (isifungo ukuthi bazobuya naye) wathi “uMvelinqangi ungufakazi kulokhu esikushoyo”"